{"article_id":"7w8Ya8zw1ut6h99H","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump is preparing to add more countries to his six-nation travel ban executive order","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"- though he ' ll likely impose lesser penalties such as additional traveler screening on them ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"administration officials said Friday .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"The officials also declared victory from the original travel ban ,","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that the process has pushed a number of other countries to begin sharing more information about their citizens","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"who are seeking visas","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to enter the U.S .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"The crux of the travel ban","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"- a 90-day pause on some admissions from six terrorist-connected -","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"is slated to expire Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and White House , Homeland Security and State Department officials said Friday","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"they ' re looking to update it .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Homeland Security Secretary Elaine Duke has submitted a set of recommendations to Mr. Trump for countries","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that should still face travel restrictions","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"or whose travelers will face \" enhanced screening . \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Mr. Trump is pondering the recommendations ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and officials declined Friday to talk","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"about which countries are in play .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"They wouldn ' t say","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"whether the six countries on the original target list from March","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"- Iran , Libya , Somalia , Sudan , Syria and Yemen -","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"will all remain on the updated list ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"but did say","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"others have been added into the list as less-than-cooperative .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"\" What the secretary has recommended are tougher measures and more specific measures , \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"said Miles Taylor , counselor to Ms. Duke .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"The government said","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"it went through a months-long , two-tier review of other countries ' information-sharing with the U.S.","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"After an initial assessment , countries","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"that were deemed \" inadequate \"","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"were put on 50-day notice","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"if they didn ' t promise to comply","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"they could face restrictions .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"\" We managed to get countries","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"who had not previously been sharing things like terrorist information","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"to start doing just that , \"","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"But Mr. Taylor said","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"some countries were \" still unable or worse yet , deliberately unwilling to comply. \"","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"They ' re the ones","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"that will face new restrictions .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"the new standards","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"Ms. Duke suggested","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"are conditions-based , rather than the time-based 90-day approach","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Trump took in his initial executive order .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Even before Mr. Trump ' s final decision , his political opponents blasted him ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"the entire process \" continues to be driven by religious animus . \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"\" Any nominal changes in countries or security rationalizations will not change that :","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"This order has been and will continue to be the president ' s way","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"of making good on his campaign promise","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to institute a Muslim ban , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"said Johnathan Smith , legal director of Muslim Advocates .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"The original travel ban grew out of then-candidate Trump ' s demand for \" extreme vetting \" of travelers , particularly those from Muslim countries .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"Once in office , he called for a 90-day pause in travel from seven countries","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"were too connected to terrorism .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"He also imposed a 120-halt to admissions of refugees .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"In both cases","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"he wanted to give the government a chance","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"to get a handle on its admission policies .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"His initial Jan. 27 travel ban executive order was chaotically implemented","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"and met resistance in the courts ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"leading the president to issue a revised order in March .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"The new order cut Iraq from the list of targeted countries","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"- the administration said","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"the Iraqi government earned its way off the ban","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"by taking quick steps toward better cooperation -","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and curtailed the ban","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"so it didn ' t apply to legal immigrants and some others with deep ties to the U.S .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"The Supreme Court had been set to hear oral argument next month on the current version of the travel ban ,","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"but had signaled","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"that could become moot","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"if Mr. Trump made substantial changes to the policy","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"tied to the end of the 90-day pause .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Officials","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"briefing reporters Friday said","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"they can ' t predict how the updates will affect the court case","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"since Mr. Trump hasn ' t announced a final decision yet .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"But they said","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"the Justice Department has been consulted throughout the process .","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"Supreme Court justices have delivered a mixed verdict on the current ban ,","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"ruling","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that Mr. Trump does have important national security powers","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that must be respected ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"but finding","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"that in cases","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"where the would-be visitor has \" bona fide \" ties to a person or institution in the U.S. ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"they have rights","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that must also be respected .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Under that framework ,","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"the justices said ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"the administration was free to block some travel ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"but had to admit refugees worldwide , and visitors from the six targeted countries ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"if they proved those ties .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"That set off a new round of litigation","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"over whether grandparents or cousins counted as \" close \" relations ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"and whether having a refugee case","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"assigned to a resettlement agency in the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"was a \" bona fide \" relationship .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"The administration capitulated on the family issue ,","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"but won another victory in the Supreme Court on the refugee side .","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Under the calendar","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"Mr. Trump laid out in his executive order ,","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"the refugee ban runs for another month .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":217,"left":182,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":116,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":111,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":110,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":3,"right":114,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":4,"right":113,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":113,"left":5,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":163,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":155,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":120,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":118,"right":119,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":117,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":125,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":13,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":130,"right":152,"relation":"elaboratio